        "Interpretation: Evening rush hours (16–18) are the busiest, with trip counts peaking around 6 PM. Average fares are slightly lower than mid‑afternoon, but tip percentages are consistently high (≈22%), showing strong demand and higher tipping during commuter peaks.\n",
