        "\n",
        "Query 2- Shows which day has fastest average trips\n",
        "\n",
        "Interpretation: Tuesday has the highest average trip speed (≈17.5 mph), with moderate distances and durations. This suggests lighter traffic conditions compared to other weekdays, possibly reflecting mid‑week travel patterns.\n",
